The Time Series Cross Validation Resamples the M750 Data (Training Set)

Source: R/data.R
m750_training_resamples.Rd

The Time Series Cross Validation Resamples the M750 Data (Training Set)

m750_training_resamples

Format

An time_series_cv object with 6 slices of Time Series Cross Validation resamples made on the training(m750_splits)

Details

library(timetk)
m750_training_resamples &lt;- time_series_cv(
    data        = training(m750_splits),
    assess      = "2 years",
    skip        = "2 years",
    cumulative  = TRUE,
    slice_limit = 6
)

Examples

library(rsample)

m750_training_resamples
#> # A tibble: 6 x 2
#>   splits           id    
#>   <list>           <chr> 
#> 1 <split [258/24]> Slice1
#> 2 <split [234/24]> Slice2
#> 3 <split [210/24]> Slice3
#> 4 <split [186/24]> Slice4
#> 5 <split [162/24]> Slice5
#> 6 <split [138/24]> Slice6
